                <p>Want to discover more local history? If so then 'The Sanderstead Local History Group' would like to invite you to our monthly meetings held 2-4pm at All Saints Church Hall, Onslow Gardens, Sanderstead on the last Wednesday in the month. A small charge of £2 each meeting to cover hall hire and refreshments. No annual fee. Information is on our web site with a link to the Bourne Society where you can find local history books they have produced.</p>
                <p>For 2021 our meetings have been via Zoom and forthcoming meetings are:</p>
